        <div class="main review-item" id="4776425">

            
    
    <header class="main-hd">
        <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/aixiaoke/" class="avator">
            <img width="24" height="24" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u1182135-29.jpg">
        </a>

        <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/aixiaoke/" class="name">艾小柯</a>

            <span class="allstar30 main-title-rating" title="还行"></span>

        <span content="2011-03-07" class="main-meta">2011-03-07 21:07:54</span>


    </header>


            <div class="main-bd">

                <h2><a href="https://book.douban.com/review/4776425/">代沟</a></h2>

                <div id="review_4776425_short" class="review-short" data-rid="4776425">
                    <div class="short-content">

                        我怎么也喜欢不起来舒国治先生的散文集《理想的下午》。  真可惜，我本来是打算将这本书当作“晃荡散文”来参考的，但读来读去，既不能欣赏那种对自我独特生活模式之沾沾自喜的优越感，也无法认同那个年代的咬文嚼字式的“古资”态度，这杯茶实在喝不对胃口。倒不是说这书写得...

                        &nbsp;(<a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-4776425-copy" class="unfold" title="展开">展开</a>)
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div id="review_4776425_full" class="hidden">
                    <div id="review_4776425_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
                </div>

                <div class="action">
                    <a href="javascript:;" class="action-btn up" data-rid="4776425" title="有用">
                        <img src="https://img1.doubanio.com/f/zerkalo/536fd337139250b5fb3cf9e79cb65c6193f8b20b/pics/up.png" />
